		<td><b>ines header required for real hardware?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Is the ines header used when a rom is run on real hardware, or is it just a convenience for emulators?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
